# Rules for Cursor Agent

## Stack
- React + Vite
- Motion (framer-motion v11+) for animations
- Plain CSS modules (no Tailwind, no UI libraries)
- No TypeScript — plain JavaScript

## Code style
- Functional components only
- No class components
- Import motion from 'motion/react'
- Keep components small — max 80 lines per file
- One component per file

## What NOT to do
- Do not install new packages without asking
- Do not touch context.md, agents.md, tasks.md
- Do not rewrite existing components — extend them
- Do not use inline styles more than 2 properties

## Before every task
1. Read context.md
2. Read tasks.md — find current task
3. Do only that task
4. After done — update tasks.md status
